ter vntd-content-element counter-color-white counter-with-icon\" data-perc=\"10550\"><div class=\"counter-icon\"><i class=\"\"><\/i><\/div><div class=\"counter-value\"><div class=\"counter-number\">0<\/div><\/div><div class=\"counter-title\">\u20ac Budget ``Kits Hygi\u00e8ne``<\/div><\/div>[\/vc_column][vc_column width=\u00a0\u00bb1\/4&Prime;]<div id=\"counter-551\" class=\"vntd-counter vntd-content-element counter-color-white counter-with-icon\" data-perc=\"6380\"><div class=\"counter-icon\"><i class=\"\"><\/i><\/div><div class=\"counter-value\"><div class=\"counter-number\">0<\/div><\/div><div class=\"counter-title\">\u20ac Budget Eau &amp; Energie<\/div><\/div>[\/vc_column][vc_column width=\u00a0\u00bb1\/4&Prime;]<div id=\"counter-895\" class=\"vntd-counter vntd-content-element counter-color-white counter-with-icon\" data-perc=\"20600\"><div class=\"counter-icon\"><i class=\"\"><\/i><\/div><div class=\"counter-value\"><div class=\"counter-number\">0<\/div><\/div><div class=\"counter-title\">\u20ac Budget Constructions-Equipements<\/div><\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row equal_height=\u00a0\u00bbyes\u00a0\u00bb content_placement=\u00a0\u00bbmiddle\u00a0\u00bb css=\u00a0\u00bb.vc_custom_1538937956997{padding-bottom: 90px !important;}\u00a0\u00bb][vc_column width=\u00a0\u00bb1\/2&Prime; col_padding=\u00a0\u00bb2&Prime; col_padding_side=\u00a0\u00bbright\u00a0\u00bb][vc_single_image image=\u00a0\u00bb3992&Prime; img_size=\u00a0\u00bb700&#215;600&Prime; css_animation=\u00a0\u00bbnone\u00a0\u00bb css=\u00a0\u00bb.vc_custom_1550184374963{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}\u00a0\u00bb][\/vc_column][vc_column width=\u00a0\u00bb1\/2&Prime; col_padding=\u00a0\u00bb2&Prime; col_padding_side=\u00a0\u00bbleft\u00a0\u00bb][vc_column_text font_size=\u00a0\u00bbmedium\u00a0\u00bb]<\/p>\n<h3><strong><span style=\"color: #0085a4;\">L&rsquo;eau et l&rsquo;\u00e9nergie<\/span><\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>Il s&rsquo;agit de s&rsquo;assurer de la qualit\u00e9 de l&rsquo;eau mais aussi de sa quantit\u00e9. AMTM finance des panneaux solaires, des r\u00e9servoirs, filtres et pompes \u00e0 eau[\/vc_column_text]<div class=\"wpb_content_element\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"vntd-separator separator-color-default\"><\/div><\/div><\/div>[vc_column_text]Chaque mission vise ensuite \u00e0 s&rsquo;assurer du bon entretien du mat\u00e9riel et du maintien de la qualit\u00e9 de l&rsquo;eau fournie, car sa d\u00e9gradation entra\u00eene in\u00e9vitablement et rapidement le retour d&rsquo;affections diverses, notamment digestives et cutan\u00e9es.[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row equal_height=\u00a0\u00bbyes\u00a0\u00bb content_placement=\u00a0\u00bbmiddle\u00a0\u00bb bg_color_pre=\u00a0\u00bbbg-color-accent-3&Prime; css=\u00a0\u00bb.vc_custom_1538935209890{padding-top: 90px !important;padding-bottom: 90px !important;}\u00a0\u00bb][vc_column width=\u00a0\u00bb1\/2&Prime; col_padding=\u00a0\u00bb2&Prime; col_padding_side=\u00a0\u00bbright\u00a0\u00bb][vc_column_text font_size=\u00a0\u00bbmedium\u00a0\u00bb text_color=\u00a0\u00bbwhite\u00a0\u00bb]<\/p>\n<h3>L&rsquo;hygi\u00e8ne<\/h3>\n<p>AMTM met en place des programmes d\u2019\u00e9ducation sur l\u2019hygi\u00e8ne de base comme se laver les mains, les dents, ne pas manger \u00e0 m\u00eame un sol sans protection, ne pas boire de l\u2019eau pollu\u00e9e. Les r\u00e9sultats se font rapidement sentir et, chaque ann\u00e9e, les m\u00e9decins notent l\u2019\u00e9volution de la sant\u00e9 de chacun des r\u00e9sidents.<\/p>\n<p>Chaque ann\u00e9e, ceux-ci re\u00e7oivent un kit hygi\u00e8ne (dentifrice, brosse \u00e0 dent, savon, serviette de toilette, taie d&rsquo;oreiller). Les femmes font l&rsquo;objet d&rsquo;une attention particuli\u00e8re en recevant des serviettes p\u00e9riodiques et des cr\u00e8mes pour le corps.[\/vc_column_text]<div class=\"wpb_content_element\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"vntd-separator separator-color-default\"><\/div><\/div><\/div>[vc_column_text text_color=\u00a0\u00bbwhite\u00a0\u00bb]Il est ainsi facile de mesurer le suivi de ces r\u00e8gles d\u2019hygi\u00e8ne par l\u2019\u00e9tat g\u00e9n\u00e9ral de la population.[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column width=\u00a0\u00bb1\/2&Prime; col_padding=\u00a0\u00bb2&Prime; col_padding_side=\u00a0\u00bbleft\u00a0\u00bb][vc_single_image image=\u00a0\u00bb3479&Prime; img_size=\u00a0\u00bb700&#215;600&Prime; css_animation=\u00a0\u00bbnone\u00a0\u00bb css=\u00a0\u00bb.vc_custom_1538934815628{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}\u00a0\u00bb][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row equal_height=\u00a0\u00bbyes\u00a0\u00bb content_placement=\u00a0\u00bbmiddle\u00a0\u00bb css=\u00a0\u00bb.vc_custom_1493822260304{padding-top: 90px !important;padding-bottom: 90px !important;}\u00a0\u00bb][vc_column width=\u00a0\u00bb1\/2&Prime; col_padding=\u00a0\u00bb2&Prime; col_padding_side=\u00a0\u00bbright\u00a0\u00bb][vc_single_image image=\u00a0\u00bb3995&Prime; img_size=\u00a0\u00bb700&#215;600&Prime; css_animation=\u00a0\u00bbnone\u00a0\u00bb css=\u00a0\u00bb.vc_custom_1550184554460{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}\u00a0\u00bb][\/vc_column][vc_column width=\u00a0\u00bb1\/2&Prime; col_padding=\u00a0\u00bb2&Prime; col_padding_side=\u00a0\u00bbleft\u00a0\u00bb][vc_column_text font_size=\u00a0\u00bbmedium\u00a0\u00bb]<\/p>\n<h3><strong><span style=\"color: #0085a4;\">Pr\u00e9vention et \u00e9ducation sexuelle<\/span><\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>Un certain nombre de nos prot\u00e9g\u00e9s ont \u00e9t\u00e9 victimes de violences ou d\u2019abus sexuels au sein de leur famille ou de la part d\u2019employeurs ou de voisins. Ce v\u00e9cu laisse \u00e9videmment d\u2019importantes s\u00e9quelles sur le plan psychologique.<br \/>\nLe sujet n&rsquo;est pas si simple \u00e0 aborder et pourtant nos \u00e9quipes avec respect et empathie, savent \u00e9couter et r\u00e9pondre aux questions. Les enfants et adolescents, jeunes nonnes sont ouverts et d\u00e9sireux d\u2019\u00e9changer sur toutes les questions qui touchent au corps&#8230;